title: Emily (Ping-Jen) Su

Bio
Hi! I am a current 3rd year student at the University of Toronto double majoring in Statistics and Cognitive Science (Computational Cognition Stream). While taking the various courses required for Cognitive science I have discovered strong interest in Business, Linguistics, and AI. To which I am looking for related research, interships, and experience related.
